-lrb- cnn -rrb- the idea of sustainable development is that raw capitalism is far too powerful for its own good .
global capitalism is a juggernaut , with the world economy now doubling in size every generation .
yet on a finite earth , with a billion new people being added every 15 years , that juggernaut is now laying siege to the physical bases of life and the social support systems that make life pleasant and decent .
sustainable development offers a path out of this growing crisis .